DESCRIPTION
------------------------------------------------
The sniffer mote is used to analise the communication performance.
to use it, we need to program the mote and run the seriallisten program, 
which is in the folder: seriallisten/


All the steps are explained on the document "Wireless Crane
Event-Triggered Control" by Aitor Hernandez, Faisal Altaf and
Jose Araujo or in the "Communication between PC and motes" by Aitor
Hernandez.